Thank you for downloading SmartSecurity for Linux. 
Lets get started! 

1. In order to install SmartSecurity for Linux please go to the install directory under smartsecurity for linux. The file path should look like the following:
 /smartsecurity_linux/install/

2.Once you are in that directory in terminal type the following
    sudo chmod u+x install

followed by

    ./install

3. You will recieve a conformation message that SmartSecurity for Linux has been installed



